Quick How-To:


  SETUP PROCESS

    cd ~
    git clone git://github.com/mattx86/symfony-aliases.git
    nano symfony-aliases/.symfony-projects.inc.sh   # edit PATH_TO_SF_PROJECTS variable
    EXPORT_PATH="$HOME/symfony-aliases;$PATH"
    echo ""export PATH=$EXPORT_PATH"" >> ~/.bashrc
    export PATH=$EXPORT_PATH

  USAGE EXAMPLE

    cd sites/projectA/config
    scc  # equivalent of: cd .. ; ./symfony cc ; cd config
